    *   *Code Draft (In-place):*
        ```python
        def quicksort(arr, low, high):
            if low < high:
                pi = partition(arr, low, high)
                quicksort(arr, low, pi-1)
                quicksort(arr, pi+1, high)
        ```
    *   *Partition Logic:*
        ```python
        pivot = arr[high]
        i = low - 1
        for j in range(low, high):
            if arr[j] <= pivot:
                swap arr[i] and arr[j]
                i++
        swap arr[i+1] and arr[high]
        return i+1
        ```

